headline: Thermo Fisher Scientific to Present at the J.P. Morgan 2026 Healthcare Conference
summary: WALTHAM, Mass., January 06, 2026--Thermo Fisher Scientific Inc. (NYSE: TMO), the world leader in serving science, announced that Marc N. Casper, chairman, president and chief executive officer, will present at the J.P. Morgan 2026 Healthcare Conference on Tuesday, January 13, 2026, at 11:15 a.m. (ET).
